Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,你的每一个细胞中，都有23对染色体。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,one from your mom and one from your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,一对染色体中有一条来自母亲，另一条来自父亲。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,And at particular places on some chromosomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,在某些染色体中的特定位置上，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,there are short sections of DNA that repeat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,会有一些重复的DNA片段，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,like A A T G, A A T G, A A T G, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,像是AATG,AATG,AATG这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,These are called short tandem repeats or STRs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些片段被称为“短串联重复序列（STR）”。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,and different people have different numbers of repeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,不同的人有不同数量的重复片段。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Forensic labs produce STR profiles
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,法医实验室通过计算所有的重复片段总数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,by counting up the number of repeats at each location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,来生成STR档案。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Initially, there were only 13 places on the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,最初，DNA上只有13个位置的STR会被计数，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,where STRs were counted, but in 2017
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,但2017年的时候，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,that was expanded to 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个数量扩大到了20个。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:18.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,It feels to me like that's not that much information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:18.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,我感觉这个档案并没有提供太多有用的信息。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,并不是你认为的这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But the chances of two people having
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,两个人在所有被计算的位置上，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,the exact same number of repeats at all locations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,都拥有相同数量的重复片段的概率
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,is incredibly small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,是非常小的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,The CODIS database now contains
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,现在，CODIS数据库中，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,over 18 million STR profiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,已经有了超过1800万的STR档案。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The golden state killer's DNA profile has been up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,2001年，金州杀手的DNA档案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,at the national DNA database
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,就被上传到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,that's run by the FBI called CODIS since 2001
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,FBI建立的国家DNA数据库（CODIS）。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,and has been searching ever since with no hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,自那以后，就一直在找他，但毫无成效。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,We did Interpol searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们向国际刑警组织申请，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,trying to search other country's DNA databases thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:49.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,尝试在其他国家的DNA数据库中搜索。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,well, maybe he came from a out of the country
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们想得很美，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,that's why after all this time we have yet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,这么久都没确认他的身份，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,to be able to identify him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,可能是因为他来自其他国家。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,and obviously we didn't get any hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,不过很显然，我们的搜索没有任何收获。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But genetic sequencing technology was advancing rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:04.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,尽管如此，基因测序技术依然发展迅猛。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Female Reporter] The human genome project was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,[女记者]人类基因组计划已经完成。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Since 1986 scientists had been mapping and sequencing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,从1986年开始，科学家们就一直在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,the three billion nucleotides contained
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,绘制和测序人类基因组中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the human genome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,30亿个核苷酸。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's anticipated that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,这很让人期待……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Soon private companies began offering genetic tests
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:23.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,directly to consumers and they provide far more genetic data
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:23.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,than what's in the CODIS database.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,I traveled to Houston, Texas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,to visit Family Tree DNA headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We'll go in the lab and we'll start talking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,about the life cycle of a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,These samples, what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So they're cheek cells. They just scrape
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,the inside of their cheek, they put a cap on it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they send it back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's like a robot ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, so for DNA extraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,we need to remove all of the protections that are on the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:57.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,and just separate it by itself so we can do testing on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:57.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Instead of looking at 20 places on your DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:06.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,these tests examined 700 to 800,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:06.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The Family Finder test is based
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,on what's called a micro array
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,and this is what a micro array looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Each one of those boxes is an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can fit 24 individuals on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:22.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,And within that box is about 710,000 positions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:22.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,of your DNA, that we're measuring, we're getting data for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,- 710,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, and they're called snips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:36.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So hang on, that's like 710,000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:36.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,individual bases, like ATGC?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- For each person, you can measure 24 on that single chip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The human genome consists of three billion bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:53.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,All people share about 99.9% the exact same DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:53.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,which means on average, only about three million basis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,differ from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,These individual letter changes are known
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,as single nucleotide polymorphisms or SNPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,So on there, are there a whole bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,of like little pieces of DNA then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:15.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, so what we have is a short piece of DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:15.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,that is specific to one SNP.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,So it's one position in the genome
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,where we know there can be a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is there any example of a simple SNP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,that confers some sort of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Actually blue eyes is a single base change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:38.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So everyone with blue eyes has this one letter change? - mm hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:38.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You can see now it's starting to scan the first box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:48.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The results of your 710,000 SNPs can tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:48.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,about your geographic ancestry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,or possible medical conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,but they can also quantify
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,how related you are to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,The genetics of having a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,are a bit like cutting two decks of cards together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,The resulting deck will share
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,about half its cards with each parent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:10.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there'll be long sequences of cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:10.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:15.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,which match identically sequences in each parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:15.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:20.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, if this deck has a kid, well then its offspring
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:20.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,will share only about a quarter of its cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:27.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,with each grandparent and the sections of identical cards
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:27.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,will be shorter, and this is how it works with DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,The more closely you're related to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,the more DNA you share and the longer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,the blocks of identical DNA are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,But to compare the DNA of two people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,you don't need to read every letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,The snips are sprinkled throughout the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,roughly every 2000 bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,So if you find long sections where the snips match up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:55.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,you can bet that the DNA in between is identical too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:55.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,by comparing hundreds of thousands of snips sprinkled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,throughout the DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,you can see where these identical blocks start and stop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,and so how much total DNA is shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Everywhere that is highlighted in blue
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,is where I share DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- With your father? - With my father
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,which is exactly what you expect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,because I should share DNA with him everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,because he gave me 50% of my DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,So this is a second to third cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who this person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you can see here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:34.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,we are definitely not as closely related as me and my dad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:34.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,because where the blue is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,those are the only regions of the chromosome
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,where we share DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We all know that these genetic tests
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,can help identify our relatives but the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:46.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,can you do the same thing with law enforcement databases?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:54.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you identify family members using the CODIS database?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:54.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You can and it's only limited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,to really first order and second order relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That means if I'm looking for the golden state killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for either his father, his brother or his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:11.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,We did that over and over again with no hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:11.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Why is it so limited?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Because you've only got 23 loci.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:15.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you wanna do proper kinship analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,you need to have more points assessed on that genome
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,to see how related you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We know the answer is behind a locked door
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the answer is behind the locked door
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:31.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,of 23andMe and Ancestry.com.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:31.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,We know that they have millions of profiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somebody related to him, a second cousin I would guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,would be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And that was very hard to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, that the answer is there behind this locked door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Law enforcement is not allowed to search
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,the databases of 23andMe and Ancestry.com
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,but luckily for investigators, there was another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,An independent website called GEDmatch had been set up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,有人建立了一个名为 GEDmatch 的独立网站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,to allow people to connect with relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,使人们得以联系到自己的亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can upload the raw data
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,你可以上传自己的原始 DNA 数据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,from any of the big genetic testing companies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,无论它来自哪一间基因检测公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,and search for matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,并搜索与自己基因相匹配的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So when we initially search the GEDmatch database,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,在我们开始搜索 GEDmatch 数据库时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,our best hits come back at third cousins
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,匹配最接近的 是他的第三代堂（表）兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,which means they shared you know, our top hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,也就是说，这个人和他共享了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think shared about 1% of the DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,大约 1% 的 DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's very little DNA that's shared
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们共享的 DNA 确实很少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,but that's a starting data point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,但这是数据的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:31.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,And theoretically, by taking multiple of these individuals that share DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:31.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,理论上 通过获取多个共享 DNA 的个体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,and building their family trees
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,并且画出谱系图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,using traditional genealogy and public source documents
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,利用传统的基因学和公共来源的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,like census records and obituaries
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,比如人口普查记录 讣告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:42.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,and newspaper articles and findagrave.com,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:42.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,报刊文章和 findagrave.com
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,you build this family tree back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,向上构建谱系图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,until you get two of these relatives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,直到在金州杀手的亲属中找到这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,you get them to intersect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们最终交会在同一处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,where now you see, oh, they've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,你会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,they share great-great grandparents together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们有共同的高祖父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Theoretically the golden state killer is a descendant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,理论上 金州杀手也是他们的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,from those same great-great grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,来自相同的高祖父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,So once I identify that common ancestor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:03.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以 一旦我确认了他们的共同祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's now identifying every single descendant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:08.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,接下来要辨认这对高祖父母的每一个后代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,from those great-great grandparents
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,and this becomes a huge process.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是个巨大的工程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:14.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,People in the 1840s would typically have 15 kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:14.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,18世纪40年代的人通常有15个子女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have to identify each of those kids
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,你得逐个辨认他们的所有子女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then all of their children
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,还有这些子女的所有子女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then all of their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,依此类推
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:23.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,So now we have this exponentially growing family tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:23.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,于是 就有了一张呈指数增长的谱系图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How wide did that tree get?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个谱系图会变得多宽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:30.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I think we had over 1000 individuals in that family tree
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:30.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,我认为 里面有一千多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,but we knew a lot about our offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,但我们对这个罪犯十分了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,We were confident he was born between 1940 and 1960.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们确信他生于 20世纪40年代 到 60年代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,We knew he was a white male.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,他是白人男性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,We knew he was 5'8" to 5'10".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,他身高介于 5英尺8英寸(1.73m) 和 5英尺10英寸(1.78m) 之间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, he's in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,你也知道 他人在加州
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's up in Sacramento in 1976.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,1976年时 他在萨克拉门托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,He's in Southern California in the '80s
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,20世纪80年代时 他在南加州
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we basically narrowed it down to about five males
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们最终将目标范围缩小到五个男性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then it's just investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后就是调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- With a suspect at their fingertips,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,嫌疑人已经触手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,this spring, they followed him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,今年春天，他们跟踪他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,to a Sacramento area Hobby Lobby store
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,前往萨克拉门托的 Hobby Lobby store
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,and took a DNA sample from his car door handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,并从他的车门把手上采集到了他的 DNA 样本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Days later, investigators recovered another DNA sample
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,几天后 调查人员找到了另一份 DNA 样本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,from one discarded tissue which registered a match
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,是从一张丢弃的纸巾上获得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,to DNA evidence left at one of the crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,它与其中一处犯罪现场遗留的 DNA 痕迹吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Investigators in California say DNA evidence led them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,加州的调查人员说  DNA 痕迹引导他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,to one of the country's most notorious serial killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,找到了美国最臭名昭著的连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Former police officer Joseph James DeAngelo was arrested yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,前警官 约瑟夫-詹姆斯-德安杰罗 昨天被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,and he is believed to be the so-called golden state killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,据信 他就是所谓的“金州杀手”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,For 44 years, countless investigators have worked it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,44年来 无数的调查员致力于破解此案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,and have failed to solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,无一成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:38.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Within four and a half months, a team of six were able
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:38.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,而一个六人小组，仅用四个半月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,to figure out who the golden state killer was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,就能找出金州杀手其人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,and that was Joseph DeAngelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,原来是约瑟夫-德安杰罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,- After the golden state killer was identified,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,金州杀手被找到以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,the flood gates opened and we were seeing every week
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,如闸门打开一般 我们每周都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,not only single killers, but multiple killers, serial killers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,不只单人杀手 还有多人杀手 连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,every week were being identified
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,每周都有新的凶手被辨认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,from cases in the '70s and the '80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,那些七八十年代的悬案得以破解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,- 'Cause, there's been over 70 cases now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,因此，调查人员现在用这种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,that they've solved this way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,解决了超过70件案子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they continue to solve them at a fairly regular rate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,并且他们依然以一种相当稳定的速率解决案件。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I think
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,并且我认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Presumably that rate's just gonna increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,很有可能这一速率只会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And there's gonna be more because it's working
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,并且将会有更多，因为这种方法是有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:16.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we are going to help find these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:16.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们将会帮忙找寻这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But the scary thing is in the US,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,you have 100,000 cold case murders with DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,全美一共有100000起留有DNA的谋杀悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,You have more cold cases but the ones with DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,总计的谋杀悬案有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,is estimated about 100,000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是留有DNA的估计在100000起左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:30.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's roughly about 650,000 sexual assaults,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:30.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,大约有650000起留有DNA的性侵犯悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,cold cases with DNA. - With DNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,留有DNA？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,It seems like a real paradigm shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,这似乎像是真正的范式转变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,它确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Multiple law enforcement agencies has said
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,许多执法部门认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:42.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,that this is the most revolutionary tool they've had
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:42.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是他们继采用指纹之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,since the adoption of the fingerprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,用过的最具革命性的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:50.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,- With traditional DNA, it required getting a sample
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:50.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,对传统DNA技术来说，它需要从实际个体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,from the actual individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,获取样本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a one-to-one type of process.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是一种一对一的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,And so these offenders who let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以这些罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,they have committed crimes and haven't been caught
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,假设他们犯了罪且从未被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they're just living their life and they're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,之后他们过着自己的生活，心里想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,well, my DNA has never been taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,我从来没被提取过DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I may have left DNA in the case
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,我可能在1975年犯下的案子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,that I committed back in 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,留下了我的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,but they've never gotten my DNA, they won't find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是执法部门没有我的DNA，他们找不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,But now we don't have to rely upon that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是现在我们不必依赖传统DNA技术了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:19.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,Somebody distantly related to that offender
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:19.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果罪犯的某个远房亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,has put their DNA into a database
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,将自己的DNA录入数据库中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they have to start getting nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,罪犯就不得不开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,because that's outside of their control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为这件事不是他们能控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,They can't account for a third cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们无法了解第三代堂（表）兄妹的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:31.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,or what that third cousin is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:31.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,也不知道第三代堂（表）兄妹在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,And so they start getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以他们开始紧张不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I've kind of wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,我有些好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,how many of these individuals recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些罪犯中有多少人会意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,that law enforcement is eventually gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为第三代堂（表）兄妹将他们自己的DNA放入数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,be knocking on their door as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,最终会导致执法者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,of a third cousin putting their DNA in the database?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,敲响他们的房门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:47.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Each person who uploads their information to a database
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:47.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,每个将自己信息上传数据库的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,illuminates the identities
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,将点亮他们周围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,of hundreds of other people around them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,数百个人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:56.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,parents, siblings, aunts, and uncles and cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:56.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,父母、兄弟姐妹、姑姑、叔叔和堂兄弟姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:01.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,A study by ancestry DNA found the average person in the UK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:01.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,一项对祖先DNA的研究发现，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:06.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,has 175 third cousins and it doesn't stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:06.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,英国人平均有175个第三代堂（表）兄妹，而且还不止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,The DNA in one person will be shared
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,一人身上的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,by hundreds of people yet to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:13.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,将共享给数百个尚未出生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:16.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Children, grandchildren, nieces, and nephews,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:16.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,子女、孙子女、侄子/孙女、外甥/外甥女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,and cousins once or twice removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,甚至是差一个或者是两个辈分的表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Realistically, each person shares identifiable DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,现实中，每个人都与过去与未来的近1000人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:28.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,with nearly 1000 people past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:28.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,共享可被识别的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't take many people uploading their data
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,不需要许多人上传他们的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,to reveal the identities of everyone living in a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,就能显示出生活在一个国家的所有人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Back in 2018, a study found that using an existing database
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,在2018年，一项研究发现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:44.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,of just 1.3 million people, they could identify 60%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:44.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,使用现存的130万人口的数据库，
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,of all Americans of European descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们能够确认出60%的欧裔美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they estimated with a database containing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们仅仅是用包含了人口总数的2%的数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,just 2% of the population, you could find a third cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,进行估计，就能在99%的测试例中找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,or closer match in 99% of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,第三代堂（表）兄妹或者更亲的血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:01.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- DNA storage is one of the things that we have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:01.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,that is really unlike anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you look inside, this is at minus 20 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That keeps the DNA good for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We have DNA samples in here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,that are probably about 15 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How many samples are stored in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:17.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Just over 2 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:17.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wow. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the capacity is just over 2 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:26.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- 2 million people's DNA stored in this one small room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:26.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,By 2021, over 30 million people worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,have taken a direct consumer genetic test,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,the majority of which are through Ancestry and 23andMe,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,which do not currently work with law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:46.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,but Family Tree DNA does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:46.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- If you ask Americans, should we have a national database
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,where everyone's logged in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- As their DNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah by their DNA and their name,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,most Americans will be somewhat uncomfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,or potentially very uncomfortable with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,But we're kind of sleepwalking into that scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- There are some people who are concerned with privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:05.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,If anyone chooses or decides
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,that they do not want their results
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,to be used for law enforcement matching,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,they can remove themselves from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I do worry about genetic information being used
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,to discriminate against someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- My biggest thing is health insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:25.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I worry about if you have somebody's DNA profile
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:25.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,and some laws enacted, it gets in the wrong hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they say that this person has a proclivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,they're headed towards Parkinson's,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,they're headed towards this, headed towards that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then rates skyrocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the biggest place that I see as a privacy concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Once your genetic information is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not like a credit card where you can get a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah you're giving away something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,that you don't know what it can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, yeah our information isn't ours
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the first place. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Our information is shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes with your relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:59.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes. - And although you may be
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,adverse to this sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,if they've already done it, if it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,you know, in a way you're out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,- In society today, you have very clearly had two camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,There are those that are very comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,having their genome available to be able to be searched
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,for law enforcement purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there are others that are not comfortable at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,and that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The problem is of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,those people who don't want theirs to be searchable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,could have their DNA uploaded inadvertently
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,by their relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,So like, if I don't want my DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,to be searchable by law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,but my sister uploads hers, - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's almost as good as me doing it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Right now, Family Tree DNA's policy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:50.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,is we only accept samples from law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:50.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,under certain circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:57.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,It has to be a sexual assault, identification of remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:57.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:02.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,DNA recovered from the scene of a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:02.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,And we also do child abductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,So if there's a child that's kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:09.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there's DNA evidence, we will process the DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:09.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,so that they can try to find out who the abductor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Those are the only cases that we will accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:16.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:16.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:21.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Unfortunately now GEDmatch has flipped off the switch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:21.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,and GEDmatch has actually said that you don't all have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:28.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,to have your information searched without opting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:28.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:30.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Was that decision by GEDmatch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:30.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:33.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,a direct result of this golden state killer case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:33.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, it wasn't. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wanna tell the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:39.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You know, it had to do with a Utah case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:39.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:43.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Where an elderly woman was playing the organ in a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:43.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And there was an individual who broke in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,and assaulted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:48.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But it wasn't a sexual assault, but it's a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I think believed, tried to strangle her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:54.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,and left her for dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:54.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:57.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I believe he thought that she was obviously dead and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:57.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,The police I believe approached GEDmatch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,because that they were concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,that he was going to recommit other crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:06.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But GEDmatch's terms of service said
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,they would only help law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,in cases of rape or homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:15.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Her problem was that she didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:15.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- 'Cause if she died then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- If she died it would have fit the conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:18.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then they would have uploaded the sample
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:20.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:21.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,because it met the terms
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:21.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,of service and everything. - So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:24.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,They didn't take that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:24.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.79,0:22:25.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They subsequently caught the individual
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:32.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,from that search that they performed on GEDmatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:32.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But people within the genealogy world kinda got
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:38.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:41.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,their passions and flame saying that is stepping outside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:41.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,of what this tool should be used for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:43.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:46.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they ended up putting a lot of pressure on GEDmatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:46.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:49.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They flipped the switch because they got freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:49.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:50.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But at the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:50.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:52.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,it was a violation of terms of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:52.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:55.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I think ultimately led to a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:55.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everybody got zeroed out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:56.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then everybody gets to sign back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:04.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Subsequently GEDmatch was sold to Verogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:04.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I can tell you a new user today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:10.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,when they sign up for GEDmatch, about 73% of them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:10.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:14.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,are signing up to allow law enforcement to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:14.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:15.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're pretty happy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:15.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah I mean, that's, it's a high number.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:18.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's a high number.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:18.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:22.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And it suggests that people want that innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:22.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How many second cousins or third cousins do you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:25.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:25.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't know that many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:31.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Without even knowing it, you're helping justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:31.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're helping a victim's family get a little bit of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:38.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,not closure, but a little bit of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:38.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,and why not? - They get an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Partly, you could make an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:46.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,that if you wanna be an activist helping catch criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:46.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,one of the best things you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:52.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,is encourage everyone you know to be tested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:52.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,and put in the database.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:57.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Correct and you know, there are millions
