Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:00.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,of people who have tested at other companies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:00.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,that are not working with law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:06.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,And if they want to help, all they have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:06.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:10.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,is download their raw data and they can upload it for free
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:10.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:12.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,into our database.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:12.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:16.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I absolutely believe in a person's right to privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:16.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:19.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I also absolutely believe we have a right not
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:19.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,to get murdered or sexually assaulted or it will be part
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:25.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,having violent crimes committed against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:25.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,There has to be an equal balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:31.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That scale of my privacy has been taken
