Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:33.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,because of a third cousin has been identified
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:33.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.65,0:24:35.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,versus a mother who's talking
