Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:37.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,about her daughter has been murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:37.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:40.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,that scale is way the hell like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:40.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:43.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We're at a point now where in many ways technology
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:43.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:47.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,has kind of outstripped where the laws are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:47.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:52.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I truly believe that ultimately this tool and the,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:52.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.92,0:24:56.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,all the concerns with it will probably end up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.92,0:24:56.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.56,0:24:58.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,in front of the nation Supreme Court
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.56,0:24:58.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there will be a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:03.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,My bottom line message, if you're gonna make a decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:03.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:05.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,if there's gonna be laws restricting law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:05.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:09.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,to use it, make sure that you're making an informed decision
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:09.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:12.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,and not assuming what it is based on
