Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:18.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,because it really isn't what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.45,0:25:18.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.37,0:25:20.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I gotta keep a couple of million people happy
