Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.95,0:25:27.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.95,0:25:27.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:30.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And that's a pretty selective sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:30.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:31.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,These are people who are willing
