Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.70,0:25:33.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,to give up their information - Give up, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.70,0:25:33.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.15,0:25:34.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- To find their ancestors. - Yeah.
